 2012-04392012-04-05,  ,  AAFC,  , 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectContributions to assist livestock producers in Manitoba
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for FEDERAL CONTRIBUTIONS OF UP TO $10, 470,000 TO ASSIST LIVESTOCK PRODUCERS in MANITOBA with the added costs of accessing feed and restoring forage land damaged by excess moisture and flooding in 2011.
